        Para1: "Ever feel like your brain is a browser with 100 tabs open? You’re not alone. Modern life is a stress marathon, but yoga can be your pause button. I used to think ‘relaxing’ meant scrolling through my phone until 2 AM—until I discovered these 5 poses. They’re like a reset button for your nervous system, and you don’t need to be a zen master to try them. Even 5 minutes can shift your entire day.",
